	Customers Bank has a 401(k) profit sharing plan whereby eligible team members may contribute amounts up to the annual IRS statutory contribution limit. Customers Bank provides a matching contribution equal to


	50%


	 of the first


	6%


	 of the contribution made by the team member. Employer contributions for the years ended


