Thursday, July 27, 20179:00 AM ETCustomers Bancorp, Inc. is a bank holding company based in Wyomissing, Pennsylvania. Customers Bank (the "Bank") is a state-chartered, full-service bank headquartered in Phoenixville, Pennsylvania. The Bank is a member of the Federal Reserve System and is insured by the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation (FDIC). With assets of $9.6 billion, the Bancorp provides a full range of banking services to small and medium-sized businesses, professionals, individuals and families through branch locations in Pennsylvania, New York, New Jersey and Connecticut. The Bank is focused on serving its targeted markets with a growth strategy that includes strategically placed branches throughout its market area and continually expanding its portfolio of loans to small businesses and consumers.Period: periodOne MonthThree MonthYTDOne YearThree YearEventsEventDateUBS Financial Services Conference8/8/2017 - 8/9/2017Contact InformationCustomers Bancorp, Inc.,
